== Overview ==
Magnetic Actuators augment the existing mechanical systems to allow increased mobility as well as introducing a defensive routine to minimize physical damage.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Magnetic Actuator can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in [[Vulcore]].
